## Level 5 — Feature ↔ block links

**Question:** Do features link to building blocks in their descriptions?

| Check | Pass when |
|-------|-----------|
| Overview **Blocks** | Every **Dev-ready** Must feature lists all implementing `BB-##` |
| Bidirectional | Each cited `BB-##` **Features** column includes that `F##` |
| FR links | FR rows cite target `BB-##` where applicable |

**On fail:** `Q-F##-##` or `Q-A##`.

