## Level 6 — End-to-end relevance

**Question:** Do features and building blocks trace back to strategy, stakeholders, and scenarios?

| Check | Pass when |
|-------|-----------|
| Strategy | Every `BB-##` supports ≥1 Must `F##`; ADRs/NFRs cite affected features |
| Stakeholders | Must features map to `STK-##` / goals via UR → `GOL-##` |
| Scenarios | Must user journeys in scope covered by `SCN-##` → UR → FR → `F##` |
| Matrix | `5-dev/traceability.md` chain `GOL → SCN → UR → FR → F## → BL` coherent for Must scope (BL may be pending until Level 10) |

**On fail:** record in the section matching the gap (`Q-S##`, `Q-F##-##`, `Q-A##`).

