## Report format

```
V&V Report — <product>
Highest level passed: Level N
Status: Blocked at Level N+1 | Ready for 6-code/

Level N+1 — <title>
- Fail: <check> — <one-line reason>
- Open question: [Q-…](open-questions.md#q-…)

Levels not evaluated: N+2 … 11
```

When **Ready for 6-code/**:

```
V&V Report — <product>
Status: Ready for 6-code/
All levels 1–11: Pass
Next: first eligible BL-## per 08-backlog-implement.mdc
```

